Enum Ansi.Font

    Enclosing class:
    Ansi

    public static enum Ansi.Font
extends java.lang.Enum<Ansi.Font>
    Fonts defined by the ANSI standard.

    Many terminals do not support different fonts; it's likely specifying these will do nothing.

    Consider importing this enum statically: import static com.mwdiamond.fansi.Ansi.Font.*;
